'''Amal Bedjaoui''' (wavutse ku ya 27 Nyakanga 1963) ni umuyobozi wa filime yo muri [[Alijeriya]], producer, n'umwanditsi<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes?no=5843</ref>.

Yavukiye muri Algiers, yize ibijyanye no gukina filime muri kaminuza ya New York <ref>https://www.f6s.com/amalbedjaoui</ref>. Yarangije muri Institut des hautes études cinématographiques hanyuma abona Master of Advanced Studies in Sinema muri kaminuza ya Paris 1 Pantheon-Sorbonne mu 1987<ref>https://en.unifrance.org/movie/24837/a-son</ref>.  Amaze imyaka itari mike akora nk'umuyobozi wungirije akaba n'umuyobozi ushinzwe gutunganya amafilime y kandi nk'umuyobozi wungirije ushinzwe ibikino<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne_gen_cpersonne=21505.html</ref>. Filime ye ya mbere ngufi, ''Une vue imprenable'', yasohotse mu 1993. Filime ye ya kabiri ngufi, ''Shoot me Angel'', yasohotse mu 1995<ref>https://copainsdavant.linternaute.com/p/amal-bedjaoui-1970165</ref> .ahabwa igihembo cya Panorama mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Berlin<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1144674-amal-bedjaoui</ref> . 

Mu 2002, yashinze isosiyete ikora filimi ya ML Productions. Umwaka ukurikira, yayoboye kandi akora firime yiminota 58 ''Un Fils''<ref>http://www.algeriades.com/amal-bedjaoui/article/un-fils-d-amal-bedjaoui</ref> .  ''Un fils'' ivuga amateka ya Selim, indaya y'umusore n'umubano we na madamu mukuru.<ref>https://www.cinefil.com/star/amal-bedjaoui</ref>  Igice kinini cya firime gihinduranya hagati y'umunsi usanzwe kumanywa, nka Selim guhura na se, hamwe nijoro aho ubushakashatsi bwerekeranye nigitsina. Yavuzwe nk "icyitegererezo cy’ubwenegihugu bushingiye ku gitsina<ref>http://worldcat.org/identities/viaf-52019098</ref>." Bedjaoui ni umukobwa wumudiplomate akaba n'umunyapolitiki Mohammed Bedjaoui <ref>https://www.comingsoon.it/personaggi/amal-bedjaoui/184323/biografia/</ref>. 

